oracle.nosql.driver.ops

Class PrepareResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.nosql.driver.ops.Result
      • oracle.nosql.driver.ops.PrepareResult

  • public class PrepareResult
extends Result
    The result of a prepare operation. The returned PreparedStatement can be re-used for query execution using QueryRequest.setPreparedStatement(oracle.nosql.driver.ops.PreparedStatement).
    See Also:
    NoSQLHandle.prepare(oracle.nosql.driver.ops.PrepareRequest)
